{"surahDetails":{"id":104,"arabicName":"الهمزة","banglaName":"পরনিন্দাকারী","englishName":"The Traducer","enTranslatedName":"Al-Humazah","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":33,"totalLetters":133,"audio":"http://download.quranicaudio.com/quran/ahmed_ibn_3ali_al-3ajamy/104.mp3","totalAyah":9},"surah":{"id":104,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","bangl_text":"প্রত্যেক পশ্চাতে ও সম্মুখে পরনিন্দাকারীর দুর্ভোগ","english_text":"Woe to every scorner and mocker","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/104001.mp3"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","bangl_text":"যে অর্থ সঞ্চিত করে ও গণনা করে","english_text":"Who collects wealth and [continuously] counts it","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/104002.mp3"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","bangl_text":"সে মনে করে যে, তার অর্থ চিরকাল তার সাথে থাকবে","english_text":"He thinks that his wealth will make him immortal","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/104003.mp3"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","bangl_text":"কখনও না, সে অবশ্যই নিক্ষিপ্ত হবে পিষ্টকারীর মধ্যে।","english_text":"No! He will surely be thrown into the Crusher","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/104004.mp3"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحُطَمَةُ","bangl_text":"আপনি কি জানেন, পিষ্টকারী কি","english_text":"And what can make you know what is the Crusher","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/104005.mp3"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُوقَدَةُ","bangl_text":"এটা আল্লাহর প্রজ্জ্বলিত অগ্নি","english_text":"It is the fire of Allah, [eternally] fueled","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/104006.mp3"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةِ","bangl_text":"যা হৃদয় পর্যন্ত পৌছবে।","english_text":"Which mounts directed at the hearts","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/104007.mp3"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيۡهِم مُّؤۡصَدَةٞ","bangl_text":"এতে তাদেরকে বেঁধে দেয়া হবে","english_text":"Indeed, Hellfire will be closed down upon them","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/104008.mp3"},{"id":9,"arabic_text":"فِي عَمَدٖ مُّمَدَّدَةِۭ","bangl_text":"লম্বা লম্বা খুঁটিতে।","english_text":"In extended columns","page":601,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/104009.mp3"}]}}